title: Gods Rush 2 v1.0.1 apk
description:
Gods Rush 2 v1.0.1 

Zeus' lightning. Hercules's strength. Aphrodite's kiss. Command the power of the gods!


Gods Rush 2 is here, taking all the things you loved about Gods Rush and bring them into a new world! Control the elements with a tap of your fingers. Build a squad of gods and smite your foes. 

Save the world from an unspeakable evil. The power of Olympus is yours to claim!

Features:
1. An all-new combat system. Gather the elements and unleash chaos!
2. RPG elements that let you build your team the way you want!
3. Create your very own immortals by developing Heroes YOUR way!
4. Triumph in the arena and prove yourself the mightiest deity in the world!
5. Jaw-dropping special effects!

Don't wait! Play today and feel the rush!

Requires Android 2.3+
